Class BrnDataRef

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.traveltime.BrnDataRef

  • public class BrnDataRef
extends java.lang.Object
    Store all non-volatile information associated with one travel-time branch. Note that all data are normalized and transformed for internal use.

    Ray Buland
